release_notes:
This release contains many improvements and fixes.

**Notable updates**

- Correctly start Teams login when deployed via script/mdm.
- Fix issue where DoH wouldnt work with WARP.
- Fix "No buffer space available" error.
- Fixed issue where you could have no internet connectivity after a reboot when trusted networks were configured.
- Fixed DNS fallback issue.

**Known issues**

- You are unable to subscribe to WARP+ via the Desktop apps. You must subscribe first on your mobile device and then copy/paste your license key into the Accounts page on desktop.
- Localization parity with mobile is coming in a future update.
- Wired networks via a USB dongle are not excluded properly.
- DoH Subdomain value specified in plist may be overwritten with default value.

For a complete list of known issues please visit https://developers.cloudflare.com/warpclient/known-issues-and-faq
